reacs.QuantHlp: Differential c/s with respect to angle

x4freetext: The differential cross sections for scattering on 28Si
and 32S were normalized in the region of the second
diffraction maximum (Angle = 8.5 degr.) by comparing
the areas under the elastic scattering peaks for these
nuclei and for hydrogen. In these measurements mixed
targets containing an admixture of polyethylene (CH2)
were used.
